Package: BayesDiffIRT
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Fitting of Diffusion Item-Response Theory Models
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Manuel", "Rausch",
      email = "manuel.rausch@aau.at",
      role = c("aut", "cre"), 
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5805-5544")
    )
  )
Maintainer: Manuel Rausch <manuel.rausch@aau.at>
Description: Samples from the posterior of the D-Diffusion item response theory model and the Q-diffusion item response theory model for responses and response times.
  Provides also functions to plot posterior distributions of item and subject parameters and construct HDI intervals. Relies on Stan.  
